data.description: Enjoy downtown living in this charming 3 bedroom 2 bath home on a large corner lot.  This home has a great set up for either a rental or private residence.  This home offers 1,880 sq. ft. of living space.  The main level features an updated kitchen and bathroom, large open and huge bright living area and 2 bedrooms.  Off the kitchen is a bonus sunroom. The downstairs features a family room, bonus office and a bedroom suite with its own bathroom with tiled walk-in shower and walk-in closet. The side yard has raised garden beds and a beautiful, mature seedless mulberry tree for plenty of shade. This wonderful corner lot has so much potential and is ready for your ideas! This downtown location is ideal for enjoying all the fun things the area offers.  Whether it’s biking or walking to the downtown farmer’s market or Lincoln Park to enjoy the pool, movies under the stars,  golfing or baseball games.  The community is welcoming and fun for all with community bike rides, block parties and music nights.  This is a great place to make your home!
